Perfectly positioned in the CBD fringe this well-presented office space provides owner occupiers or prospective investors with a ‘move-in ready’ opportunity. Being at the doorstep of Kensington Road and The Parade and not 1km* from Hutt Street, this property is the definition of “a stone’s throw from the CBD”. 38 Dequetteville Terrace offers a mixture of highly functional office space, meeting rooms, neat and tidy bathrooms and open plan offices.

- 235sqm* NLA offering a mix of rooms and open plan
- Immaculate character façade
- Offered with vacant possession and ready for immediate occupation
- Located at the absolute fringe of the CBD	
- New carpets, fresh coat of paint and excellent natural light providing a positive space for the new occupants
- 6 onsite rear car parks accessible via White Street
- Site area of 715sqm*
- Zoned Mixed Use B – Policy Area 8.2 (Dequetteville Terrace South)

For Sale by Private Treaty seeking $1,250,000
